name: Peter Mohrbacher Style LORA
description:
This is my first attempt at the Artist Peter Mohrbacher

This is another WILD one so try it out and see if you like it.

It has alot of non humanoid figures, robot like, gods or whatever. It is very interesting so play with it!

USE LOW CFG Scale

Let it do its thing... just guide it a bit for the best results.

I know he's part of the SD 1.5 dataset but you cant really use his style on Booru models, thats why this exists.

Hope to hear your thoughts

It was trained over AbyssOrangeMix 2 Hard

All the preview images use

DPM++ 2M Karras 30 Steps 320x320 Hires x2 CFG 3-5 Denoising at 0.7

Recomended weight: 0.65
